\ Manual tdb smoke case.
\
\ Run directly from the repository root with:
\   .\build\toy.exe --tdb toy\tests\manual_tdb.toy
\
\ Use `stack` and `bt` while entering `tdb-inc` and the quotation scheduled by
\ `times`. The same file can be stepped into from a REPL `load` call.

'tdb-inc [ 1 + ] def
0 2 [ tdb-inc ] times
